  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Toy Shop Simulator\" lets you manage a toy store. Organize shelves, help customers, and expand your shop in a fun, playful world. Join our Discord to connect with other players and share your toy shop experiences! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/38b496be19104150ba129dda29cc8528.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Create the ultimate toy empire from the ground up. Design, manage, and grow your dream toy shop in a bustling city where your creativity and strategy will lead to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cbf9415c73d24364281ac8598eb318f5.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Arrange toys on shelves, optimize store layout for aesthetics and efficiency, and create an inviting shopping experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9a3bdaae0308b8ce3217386a1dd7b41d.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Customize and decorate every corner of your store to create a charming and personalized shopping environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/0037645a2c38545a3a679cb9b66bd33a.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Buy licenses from top brands to stock a wide range of toys. Add variety to your shop and attract more customers with every new brand you bring in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/54cbcef750069c42dfb603e25f2f5a60.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Grow your store’s physical space, upgrade interiors, and continually adapt to meet customer demands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/6416ae21e2b61162abccc3994b62a935.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Process and deliver online orders with a scooter, ensuring timely and accurate delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/792ebf9982d1f28a7b8bae731109a0a1.avif?t=1747472204\" width=800 height=70 /></span>Employees manage stocking and checkout, while a Cleaning Bot keeps the store tidy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ce7408da004cf74fb91abbe751712dc9.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Open cases to unlock special toys and boost your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/2516dd25385237ac3dd1fa62d7eba89d.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Discover special toys to attract more customers and play with legendary ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/94d54124d45ff2c337ec40366beda0d9.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Watch out for thieves trying to steal your toys—catch them before they escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cleaning Mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > NPC Interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Random Events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Banking & Credit Systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shoplifters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Warehouse & Inventory Management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Vibrant & Interactive City</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into Toy Shop Simulator and build your dream toy store from the ground up!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Toy Shop Simulator\" lets you manage a toy store. Organize shelves, help customers, and expand your shop in a fun, playful world. Join our Discord to connect with other players and share your toy shop experiences! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/38b496be19104150ba129dda29cc8528.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Create the ultimate toy empire from the ground up. Design, manage, and grow your dream toy shop in a bustling city where your creativity and strategy will lead to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/47357ef28b5b51cb0a0e2c2e30be7058.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cbf9415c73d24364281ac8598eb318f5.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Arrange toys on shelves, optimize store layout for aesthetics and efficiency, and create an inviting shopping experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9678c414c11fa9e4210a95268916b015.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9a3bdaae0308b8ce3217386a1dd7b41d.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Customize and decorate every corner of your store to create a charming and personalized shopping environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/a481064b79e1b3bd0a319d1a2f1ea8f1.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/0037645a2c38545a3a679cb9b66bd33a.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Buy licenses from top brands to stock a wide range of toys. Add variety to your shop and attract more customers with every new brand you bring in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/54cbcef750069c42dfb603e25f2f5a60.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Grow your store’s physical space, upgrade interiors, and continually adapt to meet customer demands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/86c255ea4ca50ec96e8a17e5362ed98c.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/6416ae21e2b61162abccc3994b62a935.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Process and deliver online orders with a scooter, ensuring timely and accurate delivery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/05d2e84697c303ae862b087f46c5ad9d.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/792ebf9982d1f28a7b8bae731109a0a1.avif?t=1747472204\" width=800 height=70 /></span>Employees manage stocking and checkout, while a Cleaning Bot keeps the store tidy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cc5aade65ae5398ca745233d2f5a9a55.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ce7408da004cf74fb91abbe751712dc9.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Open cases to unlock special toys and boost your profits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3b8b51b0c908cc5fc6b6667ba8546a27.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/2516dd25385237ac3dd1fa62d7eba89d.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Discover special toys to attract more customers and play with legendary ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/78f1870b0ae6fea69eb202250b272976.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/94d54124d45ff2c337ec40366beda0d9.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>Watch out for thieves trying to steal your toys—catch them before they escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/ec8faffab688ad6f10548c3bfc658726.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cleaning Mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > NPC Interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Random Events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Banking & Credit Systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shoplifters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Warehouse & Inventory Management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Vibrant & Interactive City</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into Toy Shop Simulator and build your dream toy store from the ground up!</p>",
